# YJSNPY
Explore the marvelous INM Universe via Python

# Examples
```
>>> import yjsnpy
>>> yjsnpy.tdn('野獣先輩')  # DEMO / Under development
YJSNPI

>>> yjsnpi.suuji(19)  # NOT developed
19 = 1 + 1 + 4 * 5 + 1 - 4
>>> yjsnpi.suuji(81, 114514)
81 = 1 + 1 * 4 * 5 * 1 * 4
>>> yjsnpi.suuji(100, 1919)
100 = 1 * (9 + 1) * 9
```
